CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1781619074
OL,3,CUK detains Russian oil tanker aimed at
OL,4,Cfunding 'barbaric' Ukraine war
OL,6,FA Russian oil tanker aimed at funding
OL,7,Fthe war in Ukraine is being held near
OL,8,FWeymouth.
OL,10,FThe Smyrtos is among Putin's "shadow
OL,11,Ffleet" of 700 vessels which transports
OL,12,FRussia's sanctioned oil and pays for
OL,13,Fthe ongoing conflict, the Department
OL,14,Ffor Transport (DfT) said.
OL,16,FBritish armed forces and the National
OL,17,FCrime Agency boarded the tanker off
OL,18,Fthe south coast yesterday morning,
OL,19,FSunday 14 June.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1781619074
OL,3,CUK detains Russian oil tanker aimed at
OL,4,Cfunding 'barbaric' Ukraine war
OL,6,FThey've moved it to an anchorage near
OL,7,FWeymouth and it cannot leave the UK,
OL,8,Fthe DfT said. They added that the ship
OL,9,Fwould be monitored for any safety or
OL,10,Fenvironmental concerns.
OL,12,FRussia has lost $4.5billion in oil
OL,13,Frevenue due to UK sanctions and
OL,14,Fdetaining the Smyrtos will compound
OL,15,Fthis, the DfT added.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1781619074
OL,3,CUK detains Russian oil tanker aimed at
OL,4,Cfunding 'barbaric' Ukraine war
OL,6,F"Robust measures and processes are in
OL,7,Fplace at the UK's border to ensure the
OL,8,Fsafe management of the vessel's crew
OL,9,Fwho will be processed in line with UK
OL,10,Fimmigration law if they disembark from
OL,11,Fthe vessel.
OL,13,F"They will be subject to comprehensive
OL,14,Fsecurity checks and where an
OL,15,Findividual is assessed as presenting a
OL,16,Frisk to our country, we will take
OL,17,Fswift and robust action," the DfT said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,404,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1781619074
OL,3,CUK detains Russian oil tanker aimed at
OL,4,Cfunding 'barbaric' Ukraine war
OL,6,FTransport Secretary, Heidi Alexander
OL,7,Fsaid: "Today, I took the decision to
OL,8,Fdetain a sanctioned shadow fleet
OL,9,Fvessel travelling through the Channel,
OL,10,Fcarrying the Russian oil which helps
OL,11,Ffund Putin's barbaric war in Ukraine.
OL,13,F"The UK Government stands ready to
OL,14,Ftake all necessary action to protect
OL,15,FUK waters and strengthen our national
OL,16,Fsecurity and will continue to stand
OL,17,Fshoulder-to-shoulder with our
OL,18,Finternational allies to suffocate
OL,19,FPutin's war machine."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
